I have posted some new documentation.  It includes sections on building 
applications, troubleshooting problems, and documents the C++ code.  It 
is still very much a work in progress, but may be useful even though 
incomplete.  In particular, I included a section on troubleshooting 
ct2ctml conversion problems.

It is at http://cantera.sourceforge.net/ref/index.html
